{
  "graph_id": "g01",
  "description": "Intake / Understanding Graph (thin). Turns an uploaded lecture PDF into the approved boundary input for the Research Graph. SINGLE SOURCE OF TRUTH for the node sequence — g01_flow.py and the orchestrator prompt must agree with this manifest. Reviewers are runs of ONE physical agent (g01-a10-output-reviewer) with a per-node review_profile; the user intake gate is an orchestrator step. Producers are no-op stubs in the wiring harness; the thin exit bundle is a minimal valid research_graph_input@1.",
  "orchestrator": "g01-orchestrate-intake",
  "reviewer": "g01-a10-output-reviewer",
